headline: Can Amex’s 23% 2025 Rally Be Justified After Recent Travel Partnerships?
summary: Curious whether American Express stock is a smart buy right now? Let’s dig into what the numbers and market momentum are really telling us. Shares have surged 16.3% over the last month and are up a remarkable 23.3% year-to-date, building on a robust 26.9% gain in the past year. Much of this recent upward movement has been driven by a wave of optimism around consumer spending and positive headlines highlighting American Express’s strategic partnerships with travel and lifestyle brands...
